ough it can be messy if you're not careful) into the same tanks that were used to decontaminate them like animals. The only way it could be more awesome is if they were whistling the "New Morning" theme as well.<ul><li> Cthulhu kept a grudge. And responded promptly and explosively.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DirtyCoward" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DirtyCoward">Dirty Coward</a>: Nishi and Inaba.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DrivenToSuicide" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DrivenToSuicide">Driven to Suicide</a>: Kishimoto ended up in the game after slitting her wrists in her bathtub. Sakurai also was on the way to this, changing his mind when Sakata showed him another resolution.<ul><li> In the anime, <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Nishi</span></li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EnergyWeapon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EnergyWeapon">Energy Weapon</a>: The Thousand Arm Buddha statue's weapon.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EverybodysDeadDave" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EverybodysDeadDave">Everybody's Dead, Dave</a>: After <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">the Buddha alien mission, Kurono</span> is the only team member left alive.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Expy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Expy">Expy</a>: <a class="urllink" href="http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20081107172425/gantz/images/thumb/f/f1/Sei.jpg/276px-Sei.jpg">Sei Sakuraoka<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a><small>&loz;</small> of <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/TombRaider" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/TombRaider">Lara Croft</a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EyeScream" titl